description:
Over 10 million people have already installed the free My lifecell app to conveniently manage their expenses and mobile accounts. Additionally, exciting surprises await you in the Shake&Win section!
With the My lifecell app, you can:
- Check your remaining gigabytes, minutes, and SMS;
- Choose an advantageous tariff plan or change your existing one;
- Check your account balance and top up without any fees;
- Obtain detailed reports on your expenses;
- Quickly view your balances using a widget;
- Win gifts in the Shake&Win section;
- Enjoy special offers in the 'My Rewards' section;
- Manage your services;
- Replace your SIM with an eSIM (if your smartphone supports this feature);
- Set up auto-pay for your tariff plan;
- Add family members' numbers and monitor their balances;
- Earn bonus cashback for timely payments with SIMagochi;
- Locate the nearest lifecell stores;
- Reach out to customer support through your preferred method, and much more.
Join the millions of users benefiting from My lifecell!
Stand with Ukraine
